<C>__{tommy}
<D>__{the others?}
<C>__{mrs. juba}
<D>__{they call it a "cancer cluster." oh, at first, none of us in the neighborhood wanted to believe it, but then we all saw it for me, it was when the two year old across the street developed a brain tumor, same as mickey. we looked at everything the water, the air, dump sites, insects, you name it. but we didn't have to look that far. it was staring us in the face.}
<C>__{tommy}
<D>__{what?}
